RSI Howling Moon Awnings                                                             From $1090.00 inc GST – Quote Required

RSI has teamed up with Howling Moon To offer their full range of awnings. 

These Awning are available in a 2m or 2.5M length and a 4panel or 6panel configuration. 

For EVO Canopies we recommend the 4Panel 2m Awning or the 2.5m 4Panel Awning. 

Ask the team for a quote and package!

 

Click here to view the entire range of RSI SmartCap Evo Canopies available!

Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!

 

Please note: Depending on stock & availability, the current wait time for this product is approx. 30 – 90 days from date of order.
